original: Niyataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naniyato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā … tīṇi.
analyzed: niyatam dhammam paṭicca na niyataḥ dhammaḥ uppajjati hetu paccayā tīṇi

original: Aniyataṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naniyato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
analyzed: aniyatam dhammam paṭicca na niyataḥ dhammaḥ uppajjati hetu paccayā

original: Niyatañca aniyatañca dhammaṁ paṭicca naniyato dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
analyzed: niyatam ca aniyatam ca dhammam paṭicca na niyataḥ dhammaḥ uppajjati hetu paccayā

original: Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve …pe… vipāke ekaṁ …pe… avigate pañca.
analyzed: hetuyā pañca ārammaṇe dve pe vipāke ekam pe avigate pañca
